msgid "Secret of zerotier client. Displayed masked for security; paste a new identity.secret to replace it, or clear the field to remove it (a new identity is generated on next start)."
msgstr "客户端密钥（identity.secret）。为安全起见显示为掩码；粘贴新密钥可替换，清空输入框则删除（下次启动时自动生成新身份）。"

